# Testing & CI  
- Lint code with ESLint + Prettier before commit.  
- Unit tests under `apps/auth/tests`, `apps/api/tests`.  
- Integration tests run via `docker-compose -f docker-compose.test.yml up --build`.  
- GitHub Actions CI job: run lint → run tests → only merge/deploy when passing.  
- Block merges to `main` if tests fail or lint errors exist.